Description:
You arrive at a camp and see another squid-head resting, as you approach he says:

"Hello adventurers, I see you have met my brother, I am Nezglekt first mate of the Tsnemo's merchant ship, on a mission to reconnoiter these lands and collect interesting objects. I already have a delivery ready but I am exhausted from the heat.

I see in your future that you will meet Captain Tsnemo, if you bring him this package from me I will be able to accompany you on your future travels."
DescriptionAction: Only one of you can carry the package in its accessory slot.
